    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/8f810605184f811fa4dbb533b2073e76.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 /></span><br><br>《我的孩子：生命之泉》是一款根据真实事件改编的模拟养成类游戏，在游戏中，玩家除了能透过选择来决定孩子的感受、人格养成以及世界观之外，在养育孩子的过程，也必须工作赚钱、烹饪、手工艺以及陪孩子们玩耍，改编自真实事件的精彩故事等待你的探索。<br><br><strong>游戏人物介绍 </strong><br>你可以选择领养男孩：克劳斯或是女孩：卡琳，帮助他们度过儿时这段最艰难的时光，经历男孩女孩不同的成长经历，给予他们正确的指导与呵护。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/81fb403fc5dc2a3003a9f8772dea2151.avif?t=1689284673\" width=497 height=359 /></span><br><br><strong>生活互动日常</strong><br>游戏中充满真实的模拟养成元素，每日合理安排时间进行相对应的日常，可以拉近和孩子的距离，打开他们的心扉，解锁更多剧情和人物性格的成长。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/cb0caf00fc3a84ad1051d920649dae33.poster.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/cb0caf00fc3a84ad1051d920649dae33.webm?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/cb0caf00fc3a84ad1051d920649dae33.mp4?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>照顾孩子也是身为监护人的你最重要的工作之一，带孩子料理食物、洗澡、上学、购物，此外，你也得上班赚钱还有说故事给孩子听、替孩子缝补衣物，尤其是写信替孩子寻找真相联系到亲人。多多互动才能解锁更多的内容喔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/eea303ed64feffad770a34f89de755f2.poster.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/eea303ed64feffad770a34f89de755f2.webm?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/eea303ed64feffad770a34f89de755f2.mp4?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>休闲娱乐活动</strong><br>在孩子们遭到欺负，心情不好得时候，别忘记多花点时间陪伴他们玩耍，有许多的娱乐活动能让他们再次开心起来，重新拾起勇气去和他人交流。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/f5f58eefbb347b4a7866d61e007d348a.poster.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/f5f58eefbb347b4a7866d61e007d348a.webm?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/f5f58eefbb347b4a7866d61e007d348a.mp4?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以与孩子拍球、钓鱼、画画、野外采摘、制作蛋糕，还能在特殊节日送孩子礼物，谁又能拒绝礼物的诱惑呢？相信孩子一定会很快乐的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/765d2fb7ef30d83e4ddec540eb625a2a.poster.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/765d2fb7ef30d83e4ddec540eb625a2a.webm?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/765d2fb7ef30d83e4ddec540eb625a2a.mp4?t=1689284673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>成长道路指引</strong><br>因为孩子们被下了”罪恶“血统的标签，他们总是会遭到来自莫名的欺辱、排挤，你需要做的就是耐心的陪伴，与他们对话并进入他们的内心，消除他们的自卑和恐惧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/53b6382fa10943659b28a3def7feaea4.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1114070/extras/b3b3531f485b87ad098d1ddb5cbdd897.avif?t=1689284673\" width=530 height=298 /></span><br><br><strong>游戏获奖殊荣</strong><br>本作曾获得“Bafta英国电影学院——超越娱乐游戏奖”、<i>“TapTap2018最佳剧情奖”</i>、<i>“挪威国家游戏2018最佳小屏游戏奖”</i>、<i>“金茶奖2019最佳独立游戏奖”</i>等多个奖项，以丰富的剧情和真切的情感体验备受玩家好评。<br><br>你准备好一起透过本作感受养育孩子的酸甜苦辣了吗？",
